   - Successfully implemented full quote premium calculation with all modifiers
   - Policy-level vs item-level modifier distinction: item surcharges (cursed, enchantment) apply to individual item base premiums; policy modifiers (loyalty, first insurance, follow-up) apply to policy base premium (sum of all item base premiums)
